Class LayeredSimpleParser

java.lang.Object
  agg.parser.AbstractParser

          agg.parser.LayeredSimpleParser
All Implemented Interfaces:
Parser, java.lang.Runnable
public class LayeredSimpleParser
extends SimpleParser

This class provides a parser which works without critical pair analysis. So a simple backtracking algorithm is implemented. The only optimization can made by the layer function.
